OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOutbreaks of rain possible over
OL,6,Fthe Isles but for many a dry day with
OL,7,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Strong
OL,8,Fwinds at times but especially near the
OL,9,Fcoast where there will be coastal
OL,10,Fgales.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLargely dry start with clear
OL,13,Fspells, then turning cloudy through
OL,14,Fthe evening with outbreaks of rain,
OL,15,Fwhich continue overnight and may be
OL,16,Fheavy at times. Breezy, strong winds
OL,17,Fnear coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
