OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA cloudy day with heavy and
OL,6,Foften persistent outbreaks of rain.
OL,7,FWinds becoming strong across all parts
OL,8,Fwith a risk of gales, especially near
OL,9,Fcoasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,12,Fspells on Monday with scattered
OL,13,Fshowers. Dry with sunny spells
OL,14,FTuesday. Mostly cloudy Wednesday with
OL,15,Fheavy rain at times. Winds light
OL,16,FMonday then breezy on Tuesday and
OL,17,FWednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
